# Equipment Bonding

A sword is just metal until you've fought with it through a hundred battles. Armor becomes more than leather and mail after it's saved your life repeatedly. Equipment bonding represents this truth—the deep connection that develops between adventurer and gear through shared experience, repeated use, and accumulated trust.

