### Bonding Multiple Items

You can bond with multiple pieces of equipment simultaneously, but bonding progresses separately for each item:

**Weapon at 40 uses (approaching Bonded)** + **Armor at 15 uses (past Familiar)** + **Shield at 8 uses (not yet Familiar)**

Track uses independently. Different equipment bonds at different rates based on how frequently you use each piece.

